<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 10:08:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“新篇​​章”：贝埃里基布兹的居民开始临时搬到哈泽里姆基布兹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-kibbutz-beeri-begin-temporary-move-to-kibbutz-hatzerim-in-southern-israel/00000191-92de-d302-add5-9bded48b0000</link><description>到目前为止，Be&amp;#39;eri 社区已经拥有了南部基布兹专门建造的约 300 套住房中的 60 套。 “与哈泽里姆成员的共同努力……让我们充满希望，”贝埃里基布兹的秘书说道</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 09:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/residents-of-kibbutz-beeri-begin-temporary-move-to-kibbutz-hatzerim-in-southern-israel/00000191-92de-d302-add5-9bded48b0000</guid></item><item><title>据军方称，巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军预备役军人杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-in-west-bank-by-idf-reservists-according-to-the-army/00000191-92aa-d336-a991-f6fa8bd30000</link><description>根据以色列国防军的初步调查，该男子在与定居者发生冲突后在埃弗拉特定居点附近被以色列预备役军人开枪射杀。一名巴勒斯坦市政负责人却表示，便衣定居者进入村庄并不分青红皂白地开枪</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 08:56:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-killed-in-west-bank-by-idf-reservists-according-to-the-army/00000191-92aa-d336-a991-f6fa8bd30000</guid></item><item><title>战时条件使加沙儿童脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种项目变得复杂</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/war-time-conditions-complicate-project-to-vaccinate-gazan-children-against-polio/00000191-903e-d302-add5-9bbefc300000</link><description>为约 640,000 名 10 岁以下儿童接种疫苗的计划背后的卫生组织担心，加沙地带的条件将导致疫苗的分发变得困难，因为疫苗需要两剂并需要冷藏</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 03:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/war-time-conditions-complicate-project-to-vaccinate-gazan-children-against-polio/00000191-903e-d302-add5-9bbefc300000</guid></item><item><title>地区战争暂时避免，但军队仍无视以色列北部的现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-cant-prevent-normalized-chaos-in-the-north/00000191-9036-d13a-ab93-d8b740360000</link><description>成功挫败真主党的袭击象征着以色列在 10 月 7 日所严重缺乏的情报和作战优势 ■ 本格维尔对圣殿山的挑衅是一场复杂游戏的一部分 — — 其中一些是与内塔尼亚胡协调的</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-preemptive-strike-against-hezbollah-cant-prevent-normalized-chaos-in-the-north/00000191-9036-d13a-ab93-d8b740360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击约旦河西岸，五名巴勒斯坦人丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-one-killed-three-wounded-by-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank/00000191-91a0-d302-add5-9bb4e4960000</link><description>军方表示，巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军预备役军人杀害。 ■ 美国高级将领表示，以色列与真主党交火后，更广泛战争的风险略有缓解。 ■ 本格维尔推动新的圣殿山政策；总理办公室：哈马斯呼吁西岸升级，现状不变 ■ 伊朗外长表示，德黑兰对以色列的反应将是“明确的、经过深思熟虑的和准确的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 02:31:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article-live/palestinians-one-killed-three-wounded-by-israeli-settlers-in-west-bank/00000191-91a0-d302-add5-9bb4e4960000</guid></item><item><title>法院规定，必须允许反 LGBTQ、极端正统团体在以色列校园开展活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/anti-lgbt-ultra-orthodox-group-must-be-allowed-to-operate-on-israeli-campus-court-rules/00000191-8fc3-d13a-ab93-dff7f75c0000</link><description>在海法地方法院裁定以色列理工学院不能限制反 LGBTQ 选择家庭组织的活动后，该大学表示将“继续采取行动，确保校园安全、包容并支持每个人”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 21:23:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-27/ty-article/.premium/anti-lgbt-ultra-orthodox-group-must-be-allowed-to-operate-on-israeli-campus-court-rules/00000191-8fc3-d13a-ab93-dff7f75c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法部长与高等法院院长就继任者任命发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-clashes-with-high-court-president-over-successors-appointment/00000191-9040-d336-a991-f6d054600000</link><description>司法部长莱文的提议挑战了资历制度，即任职时间最长的法官自动被任命为最高法院院长。莱文称其为“公平妥协”，但批评者称其为“政治和法律暴行”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 20:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/justice-minister-clashes-with-high-court-president-over-successors-appointment/00000191-9040-d336-a991-f6d054600000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普与以色列犹太至上主义者的邪恶联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</link><description>下一届美国总统任期可能是以色列历史上影响最大的一届：以色列人和巴勒斯坦人再也负担不起特朗普给内塔尼亚胡的空白支票</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 18:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/trumps-unholy-alliance-with-israels-jewish-supremacists/00000191-8f7f-d302-add5-9fff52da0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党袭击未能引发全面战争后，美国看到了以色列与哈马斯谈判的前进方向</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</link><description>拜登政府官员认为，避免以色列与真主党发生广泛冲突会加剧辛瓦尔的孤立和谈判灵活性的压力。然而，关键问题，特别是以色列在加沙-埃及边境的存在仍未解决</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:30:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/after-hezbollah-attack-failed-to-spark-all-out-war-u-s-sees-path-forward-for-gaza-talks/00000191-8f94-dd8c-addd-bff445990000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方因计划放映有关以色列国防军在西岸活动的电影而关闭了阿拉伯犹太党总部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</link><description>警方关闭了哈达什党的海法分部，原因是计划放映一部有关以色列军事活动的电影，他们声称该电影在以色列被禁止——而事实上，以色列法院已禁止放映同一导演于 2002 年创作的一部电影</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 17:19:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-shutter-arab-jewish-partys-hq-over-film-screening-on-idf-activity-in-jenin/00000191-8f89-dc4a-a59b-bfa94c900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 325 天：以色列国防军下令撤离后，联合国在加沙的援助活动停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-325-un-aid-activity-in-gaza-halts-after-idf-evacuation-orders/00000191-8f97-d1d8-a9f9-9f972d620001</link><description>在开罗停战谈判中，埃及否认以色列声称其与加沙边境下的任何隧道都可用于走私的说法，重申不会接受以色列在费城走廊或拉法过境点的军事存在 ■ 警察部长本-格维尔声称有新的允许犹太人在圣殿山祈祷的政策 ■ 皇家约旦航空将从周二开始恢复飞往贝鲁特的航班 ■ 战争结束 325 天后，您需要了解以下信息</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 16:59:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-325-un-aid-activity-in-gaza-halts-after-idf-evacuation-orders/00000191-8f97-d1d8-a9f9-9f972d620001</guid></item><item><title>以色列著名歌手加入反对内塔尼亚胡政府举办的 10 月 7 日纪念活动的行列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/famed-singer-joins-mounting-opposition-to-netanyahu-government-run-oct-7-memorial/00000191-8eb4-dd8c-addd-bff40f070000</link><description>以色列演员兼歌手伊丹·阿梅迪作为以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙战斗中受重伤，他与其他名人和媒体人物一起反对利库德集团部长举行国营仪式的计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:12:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/famed-singer-joins-mounting-opposition-to-netanyahu-government-run-oct-7-memorial/00000191-8eb4-dd8c-addd-bff40f070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部女子被杀，警方因涉嫌谋杀逮捕丈夫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-killed-in-southern-israel-police-arrest-husband-on-suspicion-of-murder/00000191-8ed0-dc4a-a59b-bef8d9a70000</link><description>以色列警方逮捕了 27 岁受害者的丈夫，他的丈夫涉嫌用刀刺伤了她；今年以来共有145名阿拉伯裔以色列人被谋杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 14:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-woman-killed-in-southern-israel-police-arrest-husband-on-suspicion-of-murder/00000191-8ed0-dc4a-a59b-bef8d9a70000</guid></item><item><title>资金枯竭，以色列初创公司纷纷倒闭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/its-directly-tied-to-the-war-money-has-dried-up-and-israeli-startups-are-folding/00000191-8e1a-dd8c-addd-bffea17e0000</link><description>去年，许多以色列科技公司关闭或大幅减少了活动。他们有一个共同点</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:45:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/its-directly-tied-to-the-war-money-has-dried-up-and-israeli-startups-are-folding/00000191-8e1a-dd8c-addd-bffea17e0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔是以色列新警察局长任命仪式上的真正明星</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-was-the-real-star-of-the-ceremony-to-appoint-israels-new-police-chief/00000191-8e3d-dc4a-a59b-bebdfde50000</link><description>丹尼·利维 (Danny Levy) 的任命已载入以色列历史：首次由一名已定罪的罪犯任命警察局长 ■ 警察的未来从未如此黑暗</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 12:07:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-was-the-real-star-of-the-ceremony-to-appoint-israels-new-police-chief/00000191-8e3d-dc4a-a59b-bebdfde50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院驳回反对没收反战抗议标语的请愿书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-dismisses-petition-against-confiscation-of-anti-war-protest-signs/00000191-8df3-d13a-ab93-ddf79c1d0000</link><description>高等法院法官表示，以色列警方的法律顾问已发布明确指示，反对没收标志，使得任何裁决都毫无意义</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 10:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-dismisses-petition-against-confiscation-of-anti-war-protest-signs/00000191-8df3-d13a-ab93-ddf79c1d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长取消晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-voids-promotion-of-police-officer-investigated-for-violence-against-protesters/00000191-8d92-dab4-ad99-9db292f60000</link><description>上周，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本·格维尔（Itamar Ben Gvir）非法提拔梅厄·苏伊萨（Meir Suissa）为总警司，警方消息人士称此举是卑鄙的机会主义，因为此举未经高级警务人员批准。</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 09:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-voids-promotion-of-police-officer-investigated-for-violence-against-protesters/00000191-8d92-dab4-ad99-9db292f60000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔绘制了圣殿山/阿克萨大院的爆炸性愿景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-charts-explosive-vision-for-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound/00000191-8dab-d8bf-a7f9-9fffd4540000</link><description>经常访问该地点并呼吁违反现状的国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在接受军队电台采访时表示，“恕我直言，我当选正是因为这个原因：确保圣殿山没有歧视性政策”</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 08:55:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-charts-explosive-vision-for-temple-mount-al-aqsa-compound/00000191-8dab-d8bf-a7f9-9fffd4540000</guid></item><item><title>与真主党的“反应方程式”让辛瓦尔和以色列陷入停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/question-of-response-to-hezbollah-attack-lets-sinwar-and-israel-delay-cease-fire-talks/00000191-8b62-dc4a-a59b-bbeaebce0000</link><description>真主党向辛瓦尔对以色列施加军事压力，为他争取时间来确定谈判节奏并坚持初步条件。内塔尼亚胡利用这段时间，就好像这也是他的日子一样，同时危及人质的生命</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article/.premium/question-of-response-to-hezbollah-attack-lets-sinwar-and-israel-delay-cease-fire-talks/00000191-8b62-dc4a-a59b-bbeaebce0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，以色列国防军对约旦河西岸的空袭造成五人死亡；巴勒斯坦人：定居者在伯利恒附近杀害一人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article-live/rocket-fired-at-tel-aviv-falls-in-nearby-suburb-palestinians-gaza-city-strikes-kill-five/00000191-8c67-d7f9-a5bd-be7777a50000</link><description>本-格维尔推动新的圣殿山政策；总理办公室：哈马斯呼吁西岸升级，现状不变 ■ 伊朗外长表示，德黑兰对以色列的反应将是“明确、经过深思熟虑且准确的” ■ 以色列国防军称，五个“空中目标”从黎巴嫩渗透到以色列，其中大部分被拦截</description><pubDate>Mon, 26 Aug 2024 02:06:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-26/ty-article-live/rocket-fired-at-tel-aviv-falls-in-nearby-suburb-palestinians-gaza-city-strikes-kill-five/00000191-8c67-d7f9-a5bd-be7777a50000</guid></item></channel></rss>